name: Worship to D10S
description:
This photograph was taken on the day of Diego Armando Maradona's death outside the stadium of Club Atlético Argentinos Juniors. A crowd of people came to the stadium where Diego made his debut in the first division to say goodbye and honor him. 

The Argentine people worship their greatest soccer exponent and cultural icon. Like this lady, hundreds of people were on the verge of tears at the loss of an Argentinean idol.


November 25, 2020.
Buenos Aires, Argentina
